Name: Average time from SW-Checklist Completed to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Total time between SW-Checklist Completed and SW-Awaiting AE Assignment across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time it takes for SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to occur after SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average duration of the SW-Awaiting AE Assignment activity itself (time until the next activity starts)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in variants leading to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in variants that pass through SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Time it takes SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to be followed by any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection or SW-AE Assign Reviewers) compared to the time it takes to reach SW-EIC Reject without reviewer involvement
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and SW-Reviewer Agreed in variants where at least one reviewer eventually agrees
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to the first occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed, considering only traces where SW-Reviewer Agreed appears
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Awaiting AE Assignment in cases that later involve Assign a Different Editor
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and the end of case where activity 'Assign a Different Editor occurs

Name: Time from SW-Awaiting AE Assignment to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in complex revision trajectories involving multiple rounds of review
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and SW-EIC Accept in successful submission paths that include SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and SW-AE Assign Reviewers in high-performance variants (performance < 200000)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
